quran[5{c,v,t}:
24,32,"tum mein se jo log mujarad hon, aur tumahray londi ghulamoo mein se jo Saleh hon, un ke nikah kar do agar woh ghareeb hon to Allah apne fazl se unn ko ghanni kar day ga, Allah barri wusat wala aur Aleem hai"
24,33,"aur jo nikah ka mauqa nah payen inhen chahiye ke Iffat mabi ikhtiyar karen, yahan taq ke Allah apne fazl se unn ko ghanni kar day aur tumahray mamlokon mein se jo maktbatki darkhwast karen un se makatbatkar lau agar tumhe maloom ho ke un ke andar bhalai hai, aur un ko uss maal mein se do jo Allah ne tumhe diya hai aur apni londion ko a pannay dunewi faido ki khatir qahba giri par majaboor nah karo jabkay woh khud Pakdaman rehna chahti hon, aur jo koi unn ko majaboor kere to iss jabar ke baad Allah unn ke liye ghafoor o Raheem hai"
24,34,"hum ne saaf saaf hadaayat dainay wali ayaat tumahray paas bhaij di hain, aur un qomon ki abratnak misalein bhi hum tumahray samnay paish kar chuke hain jo tum se pehlay ho guzri hain, aur woh nsihtin hum ne kar di hain jo darny walon ke liye hoti hain"
24,35,"Allah asmano aur zameen ka noor hai ( kaayenaat mein ) is ke noor ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik taaq mein chairag rakha howa ho, chairag aik fanoos mein ho, fanoos ka haal yeh ho ke jaisay moti ki terhan chamakta howa tara, aur woh chairag Zaitoon ke aik aisay mubarak darakht ke tail se roshan kya jata ho jo Sharqi ho nah ghrbi, jis ka tail aap hi aap bahrakna parta ho chahay aag is ko nah lagey, ( iss terhan ) roshni par roshni ( bherne ke tamam asbaab jama ho gay hon ) Allah apne noor ki taraf jis ki chahta hai rahnumai farmata hai, woh logon ko misalon se baat samajhata hai, woh har cheez se khoob waaqif hai"
24,36,"( uss ke noor ki taraf hadaayat panay walay ) unn gharon mein paye jatay hain jinhein buland karne ka, aur jin mein apne naam ki yaad ka Allah ne azan diya hai"
